THE RYDER CUP
September 28, 2012
Phil Mickelson
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







Q.   Tell us about that shot ‑‑
PHIL MICKELSON:   Just hit a solid, penetrating iron shot through the air and that baby was all over the flagstick, and I was really glad to see it come down the right yardage.   It looked good in the air but until you see it land, you just never know. 




END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT